Release Notes: 10:25 - 11:00, 12:00 - 1:00 PM

Hi @here *Insites Components* `v2.0.0` is now released.

Please see the latest documentation for the updates
http://components.insites.io/

*Change Log*
`Breaking change`
- StencilJS version updated from `v0.18.0` to `v1.14.0`;
- Styles are now separated from the components for theming and caching
- Updated event names to make it predictable and to avoid native DOM event conflicts
    - example: from `onClickInsButton` to `insClick`

- Methods are now asynchronous this is to avoid race condition when the method is called during component render
- `ins-base-table` is now updated to `ins-table`

*Improvements*
- Insites Component Colors is now using CSS custom properties which you can customise for your project's theme
  - Demo: https://cbo.d.pr/xxvncz

- Third Party libraries are now built-in the components
- Caching: Assets now has Cache-Control with max-age of 1 year
- Compression: Assets are now being served as gzipped
- Versioning:
  - Projects will now have an option to pick which version to use
  - Projects Will no longer be affected by Continuous Deployment from v1 that causes `403` issues

Please check here on how to migrate from V1
http://components.insites.io/#/app/migrating-from-v1

V1 docs is available here - http://components.insites.io/v1/
Insites Components V1 will be supported until `December 31, 2020`